text.__SUMMARY__: Senghasiella is a genus of flowering plants in the orchid family, Orchidaceae. It contains only one known species, Senghasiella glaucifolia, endemic to southwestern China (Gansu, Guizhou, Shaanxi, Sichuan, Tibet, Yunnan).
